860142,165,232,2,23,1,63,10,"77.‘‘ Kadā saññūḷhā pana te, gahapati, ime samaṇassa gotamassa vaṇṇā’’ ti?"
860143,165,232,24,43,1,117,13,"‘‘ Seyyathāpi, bhante, nānāpupphānaṃ mahāpuppharāsi , tamenaṃ dakkho mālākāro vā mālākārantevāsī vā vicittaṃ mālaṃ gantheyya; "
860144,165,232,44,53,1,55,7,"evameva kho, bhante, so bhagavā anekavaṇṇo anekasatavaṇṇo. "
860145,165,232,54,66,1,48,8,"Ko hi, bhante, vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ na karissatī’’ ti? "
860146,165,232,67,90,1,107,12,Atha kho nigaṇṭhassa nāṭaputtassa bhagavato sakkāraṃ asahamānassa tattheva uṇhaṃ lohitaṃ mukhato uggacchīti[ uggañchi( sī. syā. pī.)]. 
