860148,165,234,2,4,1,19,2,7 . Kukkuravatikasuttaṃ 
860149,165,235,2,22,1,89,12,78. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā koliyesu viharati haliddavasanaṃ nāma koliyānaṃ nigamo. 
860150,165,235,23,36,1,98,13,Atha kho puṇṇo ca koliyaputto govatiko acelo ca seniyo kukkuravatiko yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
860151,165,235,37,45,1,81,8,upasaṅkamitvā puṇṇo koliyaputto govatiko bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
860152,165,235,46,53,1,57,7,Acelo pana seniyo kukkuravatiko bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
860153,165,235,54,77,1,81,8,"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā kukkurova palikujjitvā[ palikuṇṭhitvā( syā. kaṃ.), paliguṇṭhitvā( ka.)] ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
860154,165,235,78,86,1,70,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho puṇṇo koliyaputto govatiko bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
860155,165,235,87,101,1,86,9,"‘‘ ayaṃ , bhante, acelo seniyo kukkuravatiko dukkarakārako chamānikkhittaṃ bhojanaṃ bhuñjati. "
860156,165,235,102,108,1,54,6,Tassa taṃ kukkuravataṃ dīgharattaṃ samattaṃ samādinnaṃ. 
860157,165,235,109,118,1,33,6,"Tassa kā gati, ko abhisamparāyo’’ ti?"
860158,165,235,119,126,1,22,3,"‘‘ Alaṃ, puṇṇa, tiṭṭhatetaṃ; "
860159,165,235,127,134,1,21,5,mā maṃ etaṃ pucchī’’ ti. 
860160,165,235,135,150,1,106,13,Dutiyampi kho puṇṇo koliyaputto govatiko… pe… tatiyampi kho puṇṇo koliyaputto govatiko bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
860161,165,235,151,164,1,86,9,"‘‘ ayaṃ, bhante, acelo seniyo kukkuravatiko dukkarakārako chamānikkhittaṃ bhojanaṃ bhuñjati. "
860162,165,235,165,171,1,54,6,Tassa taṃ kukkuravataṃ dīgharattaṃ samattaṃ samādinnaṃ. 
860163,165,235,172,181,1,33,6,"Tassa kā gati, ko abhisamparāyo’’ ti? "
860164,165,236,2,17,1,34,7,"79.‘‘ Addhā kho te ahaṃ, puṇṇa, na labhāmi. "
860165,165,236,18,23,1,22,3,"Alaṃ, puṇṇa, tiṭṭhatetaṃ; "
860166,165,236,24,28,1,20,4,mā maṃ etaṃ pucchīti; 
860167,165,236,29,33,1,26,4,api ca tyāhaṃ byākarissāmi. 
860168,165,236,34,59,1,191,19,"Idha, puṇṇa, ekacco kukkuravataṃ bhāveti paripuṇṇaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ, kukkurasīlaṃ bhāveti paripuṇṇaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ, kukkuracittaṃ bhāveti paripuṇṇaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ , kukkurākappaṃ bhāveti paripuṇṇaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ. "
860169,165,236,60,87,1,240,24,"So kukkuravataṃ bhāvetvā paripuṇṇaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ, kukkurasīlaṃ bhāvetvā paripuṇṇaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ, kukkuracittaṃ bhāvetvā paripuṇṇaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ, kukkurākappaṃ bhāvetvā paripuṇṇaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā kukkurānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati. "
860170,165,236,88,93,1,32,5,Sace kho panassa evaṃdiṭṭhi hoti–
860171,165,236,94,122,1,117,18,"‘ imināhaṃ sīlena vā vatena vā tapena vā brahmacariyena vā devo vā bhavissāmi devaññataro vā’ ti, sāssa[ sāyaṃ( ka.)] hoti micchādiṭṭhi. "
860172,165,236,123,147,1,99,13,"Micchādiṭṭhissa[ micchādiṭṭhikassa( sī.)] kho ahaṃ, puṇṇa, dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi – nirayaṃ vā tiracchānayoniṃ vā. "
860173,165,236,148,165,1,94,11,"Iti kho, puṇṇa, sampajjamānaṃ kukkuravataṃ kukkurānaṃ sahabyataṃ upaneti, vipajjamānaṃ nirayan’’ ti. "
860174,165,236,166,176,1,61,8,"Evaṃ vutte, acelo seniyo kukkuravatiko parodi, assūni pavattesi. "
