860213,165,240,19,21,1,16,2,Katamāni cattāri? 
860214,165,240,22,29,1,38,5,"Atthi, puṇṇa, kammaṃ kaṇhaṃ kaṇhavipākaṃ; "
860215,165,240,30,37,1,38,5,"atthi, puṇṇa, kammaṃ sukkaṃ sukkavipākaṃ; "
