860217,165,240,46,58,1,79,8,"atthi, puṇṇa, kammaṃ akaṇhaṃ asukkaṃ akaṇhaasukkavipākaṃ, kammakkhayāya saṃvattati ."
860218,165,241,2,11,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Katamañca, puṇṇa, kammaṃ kaṇhaṃ kaṇhavipākaṃ? "
860219,165,241,12,39,1,143,12,"Idha, puṇṇa, ekacco sabyābajjhaṃ[ sabyāpajjhaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ.)] kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, sabyābajjhaṃ vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, sabyābajjhaṃ manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti. "
860220,165,241,40,56,1,161,13,"So sabyābajjhaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, sabyābajjhaṃ vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, sabyābajjhaṃ manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, sabyābajjhaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. "
860221,165,241,57,65,1,72,8,Tamenaṃ sabyābajjhaṃ lokaṃ upapannaṃ samānaṃ sabyābajjhā phassā phusanti. 
860222,165,241,66,80,1,108,12,"So sabyābajjhehi phassehi phuṭṭho samāno sabyābajjhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti ekantadukkhaṃ, seyyathāpi sattā nerayikā . "
860223,165,241,81,90,1,42,7,"Iti kho, puṇṇa, bhūtā bhūtassa upapatti hoti; "
860224,165,241,91,99,1,56,7,"yaṃ karoti tena upapajjati, upapannamenaṃ phassā phusanti. "
860225,165,241,100,110,1,43,6,"Evaṃpāhaṃ, puṇṇa,‘ kammadāyādā sattā’ ti vadāmi. "
860226,165,241,111,119,1,45,6,"Idaṃ vuccati, puṇṇa, kammaṃ kaṇhaṃ kaṇhavipākaṃ."
860227,165,242,2,11,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Katamañca, puṇṇa, kammaṃ sukkaṃ sukkavipākaṃ? "
860228,165,242,12,28,1,140,12,"Idha, puṇṇa, ekacco abyābajjhaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, abyābajjhaṃ vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, abyābajjhaṃ manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti. "
860229,165,242,29,44,1,157,13,"So abyābajjhaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, abyābajjhaṃ vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, abyābajjhaṃ manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā abyābajjhaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. "
860230,165,242,45,54,1,70,8,Tamenaṃ abyābajjhaṃ lokaṃ upapannaṃ samānaṃ abyābajjhā phassā phusanti. 
860231,165,242,55,69,1,106,12,"So abyābajjhehi phassehi phuṭṭho samāno abyābajjhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti ekantasukhaṃ, seyyathāpi devā subhakiṇhā. "
860232,165,242,70,80,1,42,7,"Iti kho , puṇṇa, bhūtā bhūtassa upapatti hoti; "
860233,165,242,81,89,1,56,7,"yaṃ karoti tena upapajjati, upapannamenaṃ phassā phusanti. "
860234,165,242,90,100,1,43,6,"Evaṃpāhaṃ, puṇṇa,‘ kammadāyādā sattā’ ti vadāmi. "
860235,165,242,101,109,1,45,6,"Idaṃ vuccati, puṇṇa, kammaṃ sukkaṃ sukkavipākaṃ."
860236,165,243,2,11,1,52,6,"‘ ‘ Katamañca, puṇṇa, kammaṃ kaṇhasukkaṃ kaṇhasukkavipākaṃ? "
860237,165,243,12,31,1,191,15,"Idha, puṇṇa, ekacco sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti. "
860238,165,243,32,51,1,223,17,"So sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā, sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi vacīsaṅkhāraṃ abhiṅkharitvā, sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi manosaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharitvā sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi lokaṃ upapajjati. "
860239,165,243,52,62,1,103,10,Tamenaṃ sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi lokaṃ upapannaṃ samānaṃ sabyābajjhāpi abyābajjhāpi phassā phusanti. 
860240,165,243,63,83,1,176,19,"So sabyābajjhehipi abyābajjhehipi phassehi phuṭṭho samāno sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi vedanaṃ vedeti vokiṇṇasukhadukkhaṃ, seyyathāpi manussā ekacce ca devā ekacce ca vinipātikā. "
860241,165,243,84,93,1,42,7,"Iti kho, puṇṇa, bhūtā bhūtassa upapatti hoti; "
860242,165,243,94,98,1,26,4,yaṃ karoti tena upapajjati. 
