860267,165,248,2,4,1,22,2,8 . Abhayarājakumārasuttaṃ 
860268,165,249,2,19,1,77,10,83. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
860269,165,249,20,28,1,64,8,Atha kho abhayo rājakumāro yena nigaṇṭho nāṭaputto tenupasaṅkami; 
