860454,165,277,2,4,1,14,2,10 . Apaṇṇakasuttaṃ 
860455,165,278,2,27,1,140,18,92. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ yena sālā nāma kosalānaṃ brāhmaṇagāmo tadavasari. 
860456,165,278,28,32,1,40,4,Assosuṃ kho sāleyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā–
860457,165,278,33,52,1,127,15,‘‘ samaṇo khalu bho gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ sālaṃ anuppatto. 
860458,165,278,53,62,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
860459,165,278,63,80,1,142,15,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti. 
860460,165,278,81,94,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
860461,165,278,95,108,1,135,12,"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ, kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. "
860462,165,278,109,119,1,53,8,Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’ ti. 
860463,165,278,120,127,1,67,7,Atha kho sāleyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
860464,165,278,128,134,1,67,6,upasaṅkamitvā appekacce bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
860465,165,278,135,139,1,38,4,Appekacce bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu; 
860466,165,278,140,146,1,61,6,sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
860467,165,278,147,154,1,63,7,Appekacce yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
860468,165,278,155,163,1,66,7,Appekacce bhagavato santike nāmagottaṃ sāvetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
860469,165,278,164,168,1,40,4,Appekacce tuṇhībhūtā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
860470,165,279,2,13,1,68,7,93. Ekamantaṃ nisinne kho sāleyyake brāhmaṇagahapatike bhagavā etadavoca–
860471,165,279,14,33,1,84,13,"‘‘ atthi pana vo, gahapatayo, koci manāpo satthā yasmiṃ vo ākāravatī saddhā paṭiladdhā’’ ti?"
