861267,165,373,193,208,1,63,10,"evampi hi me, bhante, bhuñjato siyā kukkuccaṃ, siyā vippaṭisāro’’ ti. "
861268,165,373,209,221,1,113,12,Atha kho āyasmā bhaddāli bhagavatā sikkhāpade paññāpiyamāne bhikkhusaṅghe sikkhaṃ samādiyamāne anussāhaṃ pavedesi. 
861269,165,373,222,240,1,123,16,"Atha kho āyasmā bhaddāli sabbaṃ taṃ temāsaṃ na bhagavato sammukhībhāvaṃ adāsi, yathā taṃ satthusāsane sikkhāya aparipūrakārī. "
861270,165,374,2,21,1,131,14,135. Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā bhikkhū bhagavato cīvarakammaṃ karonti– niṭṭhitacīvaro bhagavā temāsaccayena cārikaṃ pakkamissatīti. 
861271,165,374,22,30,1,54,8,Atha kho āyasmā bhaddāli yena te bhikkhū tenupasaṅkami; 
861272,165,374,31,36,1,44,5,upasaṅkamitvā tehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ sammodi. 
861273,165,374,37,43,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
861274,165,374,44,52,1,65,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ bhaddāliṃ te bhikkhū etadavocuṃ–
861275,165,374,53,71,1,55,7,"‘‘ idaṃ kho, āvuso bhaddāli, bhagavato cīvarakammaṃ karīyati[ karaṇīyaṃ( ka.)]. "
861276,165,374,72,77,1,57,5,Niṭṭhitacīvaro bhagavā temāsaccayena cārikaṃ pakkamissati. 
861277,165,374,78,95,1,89,13,"Iṅghāvuso bhaddāli, etaṃ dosakaṃ sādhukaṃ manasi karohi, mā te pacchā dukkarataraṃ ahosī’’ ti."
861278,165,374,96,112,1,87,11,‘‘ Evamāvuso’’ ti kho āyasmā bhaddāli tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ paṭissutvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
