861383,165,395,18,55,1,209,29,"So bhikkhūhi vuccamāno aññenaññaṃ paṭicarati, bahiddhā kathaṃ apanāmeti, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti, na sammā vattati, na lomaṃ pāteti, na netthāraṃ vattati,‘ yena saṅgho attamano hoti taṃ karomī’ ti nāha. "
