861961,165,460,2,4,1,14,2,9 . Goliyānisuttaṃ 
861962,165,461,2,21,1,77,10,173. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
861963,165,461,22,72,1,112,14,"Tena kho pana samayena goliyāni[ gulissāni( sī. pī.), golissāni( syā. kaṃ.)] nāma bhikkhu āraññiko[ āraññako( sabbattha)] padasamācāro[ padarasamācāro( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] saṅghamajjhe osaṭo hoti kenacideva karaṇīyena. "
