862402,165,550,2,4,1,16,2,3 . Mahāvacchasuttaṃ 
862403,165,551,2,19,1,77,10,193. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
