863425,165,698,125,146,1,129,18,"Ayaṃ kho, udāyi, pañcamo dhammo yena mama sāvakā sakkaronti garuṃ karonti mānenti pūjenti, sakkatvā garuṃ katvā upanissāya viharanti."
863426,165,699,2,28,1,130,20,"‘ ‘ Ime kho, udāyi, pañca dhammā yehi mamaṃ sāvakā sakkaronti garuṃ karonti mānenti pūjenti, sakkatvā garuṃ katvā upanissāya viharantī’’ ti. "
863427,165,700,2,4,1,17,2,Idamavoca bhagavā. 
