863430,165,702,2,4,1,19,2,8 . Samaṇamuṇḍikasuttaṃ 
863431,165,703,2,20,1,87,11,260. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
863432,165,703,21,49,1,197,18,Tena kho pana samayena uggāhamāno paribbājako samaṇamuṇḍikāputto[ samaṇamaṇḍikāputto( sī. pī.)] samayappavādake tindukācīre ekasālake mallikāya ārāme paṭivasati mahatiyā paribbājakaparisāya saddhiṃ pañcamattehi paribbājakasatehi. 
863433,165,703,50,60,1,82,10,Atha kho pañcakaṅgo thapati sāvatthiyā nikkhami divā divassa bhagavantaṃ dassanāya. 
863434,165,703,61,66,1,43,5,Atha kho pañcakaṅgassa thapatissa etadahosi–
863435,165,703,67,74,1,36,5,‘‘ akālo kho tāva bhagavantaṃ dassanāya; 
863436,165,703,75,77,1,19,2,paṭisallīno bhagavā. 
863437,165,703,78,82,1,47,4,Manobhāvaniyānampi bhikkhūnaṃ asamayo dassanāya; 
863438,165,703,83,86,1,33,3,paṭisallīnā manobhāvaniyā bhikkhū. 
863439,165,703,87,102,1,137,13,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ yena samayappavādako tindukācīro ekasālako mallikāya ārāmo yena uggāhamāno paribbājako samaṇamuṇḍikāputto tenupasaṅkameyyan’’ ti. 
863440,165,703,103,118,1,147,15,Atha kho pañcakaṅgo thapati yena samayappavādako tindukācīro ekasālako mallikāya ārāmo yena uggāhamāno paribbājako samaṇamuṇḍikāputto tenupasaṅkami. 
863441,165,704,2,53,1,563,47,"Tena kho pana samayena uggāhamāno paribbājako samaṇamuṇḍikāputto mahatiyā paribbājakaparisāya saddhiṃ nisinno hoti unnādiniyā uccāsaddamahāsaddāya anekavihitaṃ tiracchānakathaṃ kathentiyā, seyyathidaṃ– rājakathaṃ corakathaṃ mahāmattakathaṃ senākathaṃ bhayakathaṃ yuddhakathaṃ annakathaṃ pānakathaṃ vatthakathaṃ sayanakathaṃ mālākathaṃ gandhakathaṃ ñātikathaṃ yānakathaṃ gāmakathaṃ nigamakathaṃ nagarakathaṃ janapadakathaṃ itthikathaṃ sūrakathaṃ visikhākathaṃ kumbhaṭṭhānakathaṃ pubbapetakathaṃ nānattakathaṃ lokakkhāyikaṃ samuddakkhāyikaṃ itibhavābhavakathaṃ iti vā. "
863442,165,705,2,11,1,94,9,Addasā kho uggāhamāno paribbājako samaṇamuṇḍikāputto pañcakaṅgaṃ thapatiṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ. 
863443,165,705,12,16,1,32,4,Disvāna sakaṃ parisaṃ saṇṭhāpesi–
863444,165,705,17,26,1,46,6,"‘‘ appasaddā bhonto hontu, mā bhonto saddamakattha; "
863445,165,705,27,34,1,60,7,ayaṃ samaṇassa gotamassa sāvako āgacchati pañcakaṅgo thapati. 
863446,165,705,35,51,1,122,15,Yāvatā kho pana samaṇassa gotamassa sāvakā gihī odātavasanā sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasanti ayaṃ tesaṃ aññataro pañcakaṅgo thapati. 
863447,165,705,52,60,1,76,8,Appasaddakāmā kho pana te āyasmanto appasaddavinītā appasaddassa vaṇṇavādino; 
863448,165,705,61,71,1,67,8,appeva nāma appasaddaṃ parisaṃ viditvā upasaṅkamitabbaṃ maññeyyā’’ ti. 
863449,165,705,72,78,1,36,6,Atha kho te paribbājakā tuṇhī ahesuṃ. 
863450,165,706,2,15,1,88,9,261. Atha kho pañcakaṅgo thapati yena uggāhamāno paribbājako samaṇamuṇḍikāputto tenupasaṅkami; 
863451,165,706,16,23,1,77,6,upasaṅkamitvā uggāhamānena paribbājakena samaṇamuṇḍikāputtena saddhiṃ sammodi . 
863452,165,706,24,30,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
863453,165,706,31,40,1,95,9,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho pañcakaṅgaṃ thapatiṃ uggāhamāno paribbājako samaṇamuṇḍikāputto etadavoca–
863454,165,706,41,59,1,136,13,"‘‘ catūhi kho ahaṃ, gahapati, dhammehi samannāgataṃ purisapuggalaṃ paññapemi sampannakusalaṃ paramakusalaṃ uttamapattipattaṃ samaṇaṃ ayojjhaṃ. "
863455,165,706,60,62,1,15,2,Katamehi catūhi? 
863456,165,706,63,106,1,270,33,"Idha, gahapati, na kāyena pāpakammaṃ karoti, na pāpakaṃ vācaṃ bhāsati, na pāpakaṃ saṅkappaṃ saṅkappeti, na pāpakaṃ ājīvaṃ ājīvati– imehi kho ahaṃ, gahapati, catūhi dhammehi samannāgataṃ purisapuggalaṃ paññapemi sampannakusalaṃ paramakusalaṃ uttamapattipattaṃ samaṇaṃ ayojjhan’’ ti. "
863457,165,707,2,13,1,115,11,Atha kho pañcakaṅgo thapati uggāhamānassa paribbājakassa samaṇamuṇḍikāputtassa bhāsitaṃ neva abhinandi nappaṭikkosi. 
863458,165,707,14,18,1,49,4,Anabhinanditvā appaṭikkositvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi–
863459,165,707,19,30,1,56,7,‘‘ bhagavato santike etassa bhāsitassa atthaṃ ājānissāmī’’ ti. 
863460,165,707,31,38,1,54,7,Atha kho pañcakaṅgo thapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
863461,165,707,39,44,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
863462,165,707,45,62,1,153,16,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho pañcakaṅgo thapati yāvatako ahosi uggāhamānena paribbājakena samaṇamuṇḍikāputtena saddhiṃ kathāsallāpo taṃ sabbaṃ bhagavato ārocesi. 
863463,165,708,2,13,1,49,6,"262. Evaṃ vutte, bhagavā pañcakaṅgaṃ thapatiṃ etadavoca–"
863464,165,708,14,38,1,192,19,"‘‘ evaṃ sante kho, thapati, daharo kumāro mando uttānaseyyako sampannakusalo bhavissati paramakusalo uttamapattipatto samaṇo ayojjho, yathā uggāhamānassa paribbājakassa samaṇamuṇḍikāputtassa vacanaṃ. "
863465,165,708,39,59,1,133,16,"Daharassa hi, thapati, kumārassa mandassa uttānaseyyakassa kāyotipi na hoti, kuto pana kāyena pāpakammaṃ karissati, aññatra phanditamattā! "
863466,165,708,60,82,1,128,16,"Daharassa hi, thapati, kumārassa mandassa uttānaseyyakassa vācātipi na hoti, kuto pana pāpakaṃ vācaṃ bhāsissati, aññatra roditamattā ! "
