863508,165,715,2,12,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Ime ca, thapati, akusalā sīlā kiṃsamuṭṭhānā? "
863509,165,715,13,16,1,26,3,Samuṭṭhānampi nesaṃ vuttaṃ.
