863511,165,715,23,25,1,14,2,Katamaṃ cittaṃ? 
863512,165,715,26,31,1,44,5,Cittampi hi bahuṃ anekavidhaṃ nānappakārakaṃ. 
863513,165,715,32,41,1,61,8,"Yaṃ cittaṃ sarāgaṃ sadosaṃ samohaṃ, itosamuṭṭhānā akusalā sīlā."
863514,165,716,2,14,1,55,9,"‘ ‘ Ime ca, thapati, akusalā sīlā kuhiṃ aparisesā nirujjhanti? "
