863577,165,733,2,4,1,20,2,9 . Cūḷasakuludāyisuttaṃ 
863578,165,734,2,20,1,77,10,269. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
863579,165,734,21,33,1,120,12,Tena kho pana samayena sakuludāyī paribbājako moranivāpe paribbājakārāme paṭivasati mahatiyā paribbājakaparisāya saddhiṃ. 
863580,165,734,34,43,1,85,9,Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya rājagahaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
863581,165,734,44,48,1,28,4,Atha kho bhagavato etadahosi–
863582,165,734,49,57,1,42,6,‘‘ atippago kho tāva rājagahe piṇḍāya carituṃ. 
863583,165,734,58,69,1,91,9,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ yena moranivāpo paribbājakārāmo yena sakuludāyī paribbājako tenupasaṅkameyyan’’ ti. 
863584,165,734,70,77,1,62,7,Atha kho bhagavā yena moranivāpo paribbājakārāmo tenupasaṅkami. 
863585,165,735,2,51,1,544,46,"Tena kho pana samayena sakuludāyī paribbājako mahatiyā paribbājakaparisāya saddhiṃ nisinno hoti unnādiniyā uccāsaddamahāsaddāya anekavihitaṃ tiracchānakathaṃ kathentiyā, seyyathidaṃ– rājakathaṃ corakathaṃ mahāmattakathaṃ senākathaṃ bhayakathaṃ yuddhakathaṃ annakathaṃ pānakathaṃ vatthakathaṃ sayanakathaṃ mālākathaṃ gandhakathaṃ ñātikathaṃ yānakathaṃ gāmakathaṃ nigamakathaṃ nagarakathaṃ janapadakathaṃ itthikathaṃ sūrakathaṃ visikhākathaṃ kumbhaṭṭhānakathaṃ pubbapetakathaṃ nānattakathaṃ lokakkhāyikaṃ samuddakkhāyikaṃ itibhavābhavakathaṃ iti vā. "
863586,165,735,52,59,1,66,7,Addasā kho sakuludāyī paribbājako bhagavantaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ. 
863587,165,735,60,64,1,32,4,Disvāna sakaṃ parisaṃ saṇṭhāpesi–
863588,165,735,65,74,1,46,6,"‘‘ appasaddā bhonto hontu, mā bhonto saddamakattha. "
863589,165,735,75,79,1,28,4,Ayaṃ samaṇo gotamo āgacchati; 
863590,165,735,80,87,1,55,7,appasaddakāmo kho pana so āyasmā appasaddassa vaṇṇavādī. 
863591,165,735,88,98,1,67,8,Appeva nāma appasaddaṃ parisaṃ viditvā upasaṅkamitabbaṃ maññeyyā’’ ti. 
863592,165,735,99,106,1,36,6,Atha kho te paribbājakā tuṇhī ahesuṃ . 
863593,165,736,2,13,1,58,7,270. Atha kho bhagavā yena sakuludāyī paribbājako tenupasaṅkami. 
863594,165,736,14,20,1,53,6,Atha kho sakuludāyī paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
863595,165,736,21,29,1,22,4,"‘‘ etu kho, bhante, bhagavā. "
863596,165,736,30,35,1,25,3,"Svāgataṃ, bhante, bhagavato. "
863597,165,736,36,46,1,68,8,"Cirassaṃ kho, bhante, bhagavā imaṃ pariyāyamakāsi yadidaṃ idhāgamanāya. "
863598,165,736,47,52,1,23,3,"Nisīdatu, bhante, bhagavā; "
863599,165,736,53,58,1,23,3,idamāsanaṃ paññattan’’ ti. 
863600,165,736,59,63,1,29,4,Nisīdi bhagavā paññatte āsane. 
863601,165,736,64,74,1,76,9,Sakuludāyīpi kho paribbājako aññataraṃ nīcaṃ āsanaṃ gahetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
863602,165,736,75,82,1,65,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho sakuludāyiṃ paribbājakaṃ bhagavā etadavoca–
863603,165,736,83,104,1,83,13,"‘‘ kāya nuttha, udāyi, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā, kā ca pana vo antarākathā vippakatā’’ ti?"
863604,165,736,105,117,1,61,8,"‘‘ Tiṭṭhatesā, bhante, kathā yāya mayaṃ etarahi kathāya sannisinnā. "
863605,165,736,118,128,1,65,8,"Nesā, bhante, kathā bhagavato dullabhā bhavissati pacchāpi savanāya. "
863606,165,736,129,144,1,113,13,"Yadāhaṃ, bhante, imaṃ parisaṃ anupasaṅkanto homi athāyaṃ parisā anekavihitaṃ tiracchānakathaṃ kathentī nisinnā hoti; "
863607,165,736,145,163,1,108,16,"yadā ca kho ahaṃ, bhante, imaṃ parisaṃ upasaṅkanto homi athāyaṃ parisā mamaññeva mukhaṃ ullokentī nisinnā hoti–"
863608,165,736,164,189,1,53,9,‘ yaṃ no samaṇo udāyī dhammaṃ bhāsissati taṃ[ taṃ no( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] sossāmā’ ti; 
863609,165,736,190,220,1,120,16,"yadā pana , bhante, bhagavā imaṃ parisaṃ upasaṅkanto hoti athāhañceva ayañca parisā bhagavato mukhaṃ ullokentā[ olokentī( syā. kaṃ. ka.)] nisinnā homa–"
863610,165,736,221,233,1,48,8,‘ yaṃ no bhagavā dhammaṃ bhāsissati taṃ sossāmā’’’ ti. 
863611,165,737,2,18,1,58,7,"271.‘‘ Tenahudāyi, taṃyevettha paṭibhātu yathā maṃ paṭibhāseyyā’’ si."
863612,165,737,19,49,1,193,23,"‘‘ Purimāni , bhante, divasāni purimatarāni sabbaññū sabbadassāvī aparisesaṃ ñāṇadassanaṃ paṭijānamāno‘ carato ca me tiṭṭhato ca suttassa ca jāgarassa ca satataṃ samitaṃ ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitan’ ti. "
863613,165,737,50,78,1,131,16,"So mayā[ paccupaṭṭhitan’’ ti mayā(?)] pubbantaṃ ārabbha pañhaṃ puṭṭho samāno aññenaññaṃ paṭicari, bahiddhā kathaṃ apanāmesi, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātvākāsi. "
863614,165,737,79,88,1,56,7,"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃyeva ārabbha sati udapādi–"
863615,165,737,89,97,1,32,6,"‘ aho nūna bhagavā, aho nūna sugato! "
863616,165,737,98,106,1,31,5,Yo imesaṃ dhammānaṃ sukusalo’’’ ti.
863617,165,737,107,157,1,307,40,"‘‘ Ko pana so, udāyi, sabbaññū sabbadassāvī aparisesaṃ ñāṇadassanaṃ paṭijānamāno‘ carato ca me tiṭṭhato ca suttassa ca jāgarassa ca satataṃ samitaṃ ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitan’ ti, yo tayā pubbantaṃ ārabbha pañhaṃ puṭṭho samāno aññenaññaṃ paṭicari, bahiddhā kathaṃ apanāmesi kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātvākāsī’’ ti?"
863618,165,737,158,166,1,28,4,"‘ Nigaṇṭho, bhante, nāṭaputto’ ti."
863619,165,738,2,43,1,242,32,"‘ ‘ Yo kho, udāyi, anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyya, seyyathidaṃ– ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo… pe… iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyya, so vā maṃ pubbantaṃ ārabbha pañhaṃ puccheyya, taṃ vāhaṃ pubbantaṃ ārabbha pañhaṃ puccheyyaṃ; "
863620,165,738,44,64,1,137,17,"so vā me pubbantaṃ ārabbha pañhassa veyyākaraṇena cittaṃ ārādheyya, tassa vāhaṃ pubbantaṃ ārabbha pañhassa veyyākaraṇena cittaṃ ārādheyyaṃ."
863621,165,739,2,52,1,263,34,"‘ ‘ Yo [ so( sī. pī.)] kho, udāyi, dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passeyya cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajāneyya, so vā maṃ aparantaṃ ārabbha pañhaṃ puccheyya, taṃ vāhaṃ aparantaṃ ārabbha pañhaṃ puccheyyaṃ; "
863622,165,739,53,71,1,137,17,"so vā me aparantaṃ ārabbha pañhassa veyyākaraṇena cittaṃ ārādheyya, tassa vāhaṃ aparantaṃ ārabbha pañhassa veyyākaraṇena cittaṃ ārādheyyaṃ."
863623,165,740,2,14,1,48,8,"‘ ‘ Api ca, udāyi, tiṭṭhatu pubbanto, tiṭṭhatu aparanto. "
863624,165,740,15,27,1,70,10,"Dhammaṃ te desessāmi– imasmiṃ sati idaṃ hoti, imassuppādā idaṃ uppajjati; "
863625,165,740,28,41,1,60,10,"imasmiṃ asati idaṃ na hoti, imassa nirodhā idaṃ nirujjhatī’’ ti."
863626,165,741,2,43,1,281,32,"‘ ‘ Ahañhi, bhante, yāvatakampi me iminā attabhāvena paccanubhūtaṃ tampi nappahomi sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anussarituṃ, kuto panāhaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarissāmi, seyyathidaṃ– ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo… pe… iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarissāmi, seyyathāpi bhagavā? "
863627,165,741,44,75,1,245,27,"Ahañhi, bhante, etarahi paṃsupisācakampi na passāmi, kuto panāhaṃ dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passissāmi cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajānissāmi, seyyathāpi bhagavā? "
863628,165,741,76,84,1,35,6,"Yaṃ pana maṃ, bhante, bhagavā evamāha–"
863629,165,741,85,97,1,48,7,"‘ api ca, udāyi, tiṭṭhatu pubbanto, tiṭṭhatu aparanto; "
863630,165,741,98,110,1,70,10,"dhammaṃ te desessāmi– imasmiṃ sati idaṃ hoti, imassuppādā idaṃ uppajjati; "
863631,165,741,111,129,1,104,16,"imasmiṃ asati idaṃ na hoti, imassa nirodhā idaṃ nirujjhatī’ ti tañca pana me bhiyyosomattāya na pakkhāyati. "
863632,165,741,130,145,1,90,11,"Appeva nāmāhaṃ, bhante, sake ācariyake bhagavato cittaṃ ārādheyyaṃ pañhassa veyyākaraṇenā’’ ti. "
863633,165,742,2,20,1,42,8,"272.‘‘ Kinti pana te, udāyi, sake ācariyake hotī’’ ti?"
