863741,165,777,2,13,1,55,6,"277. Evaṃ vutte, sakuludāyī paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–"
863742,165,777,14,24,1,37,4,"‘‘ abhikkantaṃ, bhante , abhikkantaṃ, bhante! "
863743,165,777,25,46,1,134,16,"Seyyathāpi, bhante, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya–"
863744,165,777,47,53,1,31,4,‘ cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ ti; 
863745,165,777,54,59,1,50,5,evamevaṃ bhagavatā anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito. 
