863757,165,781,2,22,1,87,11,278. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
863758,165,781,23,39,1,57,7,Atha kho vekhanaso[ vekhanasso( sī. pī.)] paribbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
863759,165,781,40,44,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
863760,165,781,45,51,1,59,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
