863771,165,786,39,46,1,38,5,"Seyyathāpi, kaccāna, puriso evaṃ vadeyya–"
863772,165,786,47,61,1,66,10,"‘ ahaṃ yā imasmiṃ janapade janapadakalyāṇī, taṃ icchāmi taṃ kāmemī’ ti. "
863773,165,786,62,65,1,21,3,Tamenaṃ evaṃ vadeyyuṃ–
863774,165,786,66,91,1,126,19,"‘ ambho purisa, yaṃ tvaṃ janapadakalyāṇiṃ icchasi kāmesi, jānāsi taṃ janapadakalyāṇiṃ– khattiyī vā brāhmaṇī vā vessī vā suddī vā’ ti? "
863775,165,786,92,99,1,24,5,Iti puṭṭho‘ no’ ti vadeyya. 
863776,165,786,100,103,1,21,3,Tamenaṃ evaṃ vadeyyuṃ–
863777,165,786,104,146,1,216,34,"‘ ambho purisa, yaṃ tvaṃ janapadakalyāṇiṃ icchasi kāmesi, jānāsi taṃ janapadakalyāṇiṃ‘ evaṃnāmā evaṃgottāti vāti… pe… dīghā vā rassā vā majjhimā vā kāḷī vā sāmā vā maṅguracchavī vāti… amukasmiṃ gāme vā nigame vā nagare vā’ ti? "
863778,165,786,147,154,1,24,5,Iti puṭṭho‘ no’ ti vadeyya. 
