863804,165,792,2,15,1,30,5,"280.‘‘ Pañca kho ime, kaccāna, kāmaguṇā. "
863805,165,792,16,18,1,12,2,Katame pañca? 
863806,165,792,19,57,1,238,28,"Cakkhuviññeyyā rūpā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā, sotaviññeyyā saddā… pe… ghānaviññeyyā gandhā… jivhāviññeyyā rasā… kāyaviññeyyā phoṭṭhabbā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā– ime kho, kaccāna, pañca kāmaguṇā. "
863807,165,792,58,73,1,94,13,"Yaṃ kho, kaccāna, ime pañca kāmaguṇe paṭicca uppajjati sukhaṃ somanassaṃ idaṃ vuccati kāmasukhaṃ. "
863808,165,792,74,85,1,70,8,"Iti kāmehi kāmasukhaṃ, kāmasukhā kāmaggasukhaṃ tattha aggamakkhāyatī’’ ti. "
