863837,165,802,2,4,1,15,2,1 . Ghaṭikārasuttaṃ 
863838,165,803,2,23,1,89,12,282. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ carati mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ. 
