864041,165,819,2,40,1,141,18,293. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kurūsu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ yena thullakoṭṭhikaṃ[ thūlakoṭṭhikaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] nāma kurūnaṃ nigamo tadavasari. 
864042,165,819,41,58,1,45,4,Assosuṃ kho thullakoṭṭhikā[ thūlakoṭṭhitakā( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] brāhmaṇagahapatikā–
864043,165,819,59,80,1,135,15,"‘‘ samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito kurūsu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ thullakoṭṭhikaṃ anuppatto. "
864044,165,819,81,90,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
864045,165,819,91,108,1,142,15,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti. 
864046,165,819,109,122,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
864047,165,819,123,136,1,135,12,"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ, kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. "
864048,165,819,137,147,1,53,8,Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’ ti. 
864049,165,819,148,155,1,72,7,Atha kho thullakoṭṭhikā brāhmaṇagahapatikā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
864050,165,819,156,162,1,67,6,upasaṅkamitvā appekacce bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu; 
864051,165,819,163,174,1,100,10,"appekacce bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu, sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu; "
864052,165,819,175,182,1,63,7,appekacce yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu; 
864053,165,819,183,191,1,66,7,appekacce bhagavato santike nāmagottaṃ sāvetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu; 
864054,165,819,192,196,1,40,4,appekacce tuṇhībhūtā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
864055,165,819,197,209,1,127,12,Ekamantaṃ nisinne kho thullakoṭṭhike brāhmaṇagahapatike bhagavā dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi. 
864056,165,820,2,34,1,122,15,294. Tena kho pana samayena raṭṭhapālo nāma kulaputto tasmiṃyeva thullakoṭṭhike aggakulassa[ aggakulikassa( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] putto tissaṃ parisāyaṃ nisinno hoti. 
864057,165,820,35,40,1,45,5,Atha kho raṭṭhapālassa kulaputtassa etadahosi–
864058,165,820,41,72,1,160,16,"‘‘ yathā yathā khvāhaṃ bhagavatā dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānāmi[ yathā yathā kho bhagavā dhammaṃ deseti( sī.)], nayidaṃ sukaraṃ agāraṃ ajjhāvasatā ekantaparipuṇṇaṃ ekantaparisuddhaṃ saṅkhalikhitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carituṃ. "
864059,165,820,73,85,1,94,10,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajeyyan’’ ti. 
864060,165,820,86,109,1,224,21,Atha kho thullakoṭṭhikā brāhmaṇagahapatikā bhagavatā dhammiyā kathāya sandassitā samādapitā samuttejitā sampahaṃsitā bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkamiṃsu. 
864061,165,820,110,121,1,110,10,Atha kho raṭṭhapālo kulaputto acirapakkantesu thullakoṭṭhikesu brāhmaṇagahapatikesu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
864062,165,820,122,127,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
864063,165,820,128,135,1,64,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho raṭṭhapālo kulaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
864064,165,820,136,158,1,162,16,"‘‘ yathā yathāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānāmi, nayidaṃ sukaraṃ agāraṃ ajjhāvasatā ekantaparipuṇṇaṃ ekantaparisuddhaṃ saṅkhalikhitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carituṃ. "
864065,165,820,159,171,1,97,10,"Icchāmahaṃ, bhante, kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajituṃ. "
864066,165,820,172,182,1,68,7,"Labheyyāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavato santike pabbajjaṃ, labheyyaṃ upasampadaṃ. "
