864766,165,941,2,4,1,21,2,5 . Bodhirājakumārasuttaṃ 
864767,165,942,2,21,1,88,11,324. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā bhaggesu viharati susumāragire bhesakaḷāvane migadāye. 
864768,165,942,22,52,1,148,19,Tena kho pana samayena bodhissa rājakumārassa kokanado[ kokanudo( syā. kaṃ. ka.)] nāma pāsādo acirakārito hoti anajjhāvuṭṭho samaṇena vā brāhmaṇena vā kenaci vā manussabhūtena. 
864769,165,942,53,60,1,56,7,Atha kho bodhi rājakumāro sañjikāputtaṃ māṇavaṃ āmantesi–
864770,165,942,61,72,1,54,7,"‘‘ ehi tvaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkama; "
864771,165,942,73,87,1,115,13,"upasaṅkamitvā mama vacanena bhagavato pāde sirasā vanda, appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ puccha–"
864772,165,942,88,107,1,118,14,"‘ bodhi, bhante, rājakumāro bhagavato pāde sirasā vandati, appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchatī’ ti. "
864773,165,942,108,110,1,13,2,Evañca vadehi–
864774,165,942,111,128,1,98,11,"‘ adhivāsetu kira, bhante, bhagavā bodhissa rājakumārassa svātanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghenā’’’ ti."
864775,165,942,129,146,1,96,12,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti kho sañjikāputto māṇavo bodhissa rājakumārassa paṭissutvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
864776,165,942,147,151,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
864777,165,942,152,158,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
864778,165,942,159,167,1,63,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho sañjikāputto māṇavo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
864779,165,942,168,201,1,118,14,"‘‘ bodhi kho[ bodhi bho gotama( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] rājakumāro bhoto gotamassa pāde sirasā vandati, appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchati. "
864780,165,942,202,204,1,13,2,Evañca vadeti–
864781,165,942,205,220,1,97,11,‘ adhivāsetu kira bhavaṃ gotamo bodhissa rājakumārassa svātanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghenā’’’ ti. 
864782,165,942,221,224,1,31,3,Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena. 
864783,165,942,225,237,1,106,12,Atha kho sañjikāputto māṇavo bhagavato adhivāsanaṃ viditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā yena bodhi rājakumāro tenupasaṅkami; 
