866100,165,1173,92,102,1,53,8,"Ehi tvaṃ, tāta uttara, yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkama; "
866101,165,1173,103,121,1,117,17,"upasaṅkamitvā samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ jānāhi yadi vā taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ tathā santaṃyeva saddo abbhuggato, yadi vā no tathā; "
