866107,165,1173,207,220,1,131,12,"Sace agāraṃ ajjhāvasati, rājā hoti cakkavattī dhammiko dhammarājā cāturanto vijitāvī janapadatthāvariyappatto sattaratanasamannāgato. "
866108,165,1173,221,242,1,155,13,"Tassimāni satta ratanāni bhavanti, seyyathidaṃ– cakkaratanaṃ, hatthiratanaṃ, assaratanaṃ, maṇiratanaṃ, itthiratanaṃ, gahapatiratanaṃ, pariṇāyakaratanameva sattamaṃ. "
866109,165,1173,243,251,1,75,8,Parosahassaṃ kho panassa puttā bhavanti sūrā vīraṅgarūpā parasenappamaddanā. 
866110,165,1173,252,269,1,84,9,So imaṃ pathaviṃ sāgarapariyantaṃ adaṇḍena asatthena dhammena[ dhammena samena( ka.)] abhivijiya ajjhāvasati. 
