866528,165,1311,2,12,1,49,7,"Puññaṃ ākaṅkhamānānaṃ, saṅgho ve yajataṃ mukhan’’ ti. "
866529,165,1312,2,12,1,77,10,Atha kho bhagavā keṇiyaṃ jaṭilaṃ imāhi gāthāhi anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi. 
866530,165,1313,2,31,1,253,27,Atha kho āyasmā selo sapariso eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto viharanto nacirasseva– yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti tadanuttaraṃ– brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihāsi.
