866544,165,1323,2,4,1,16,2,3 . Assalāyanasuttaṃ 
866545,165,1324,2,21,1,87,11,401. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
866546,165,1324,22,34,1,125,12,Tena kho pana samayena nānāverajjakānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ pañcamattāni brāhmaṇasatāni sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasanti kenacideva karaṇīyena. 
866547,165,1324,35,40,1,36,5,Atha kho tesaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ etadahosi–
866548,165,1324,41,50,1,51,7,‘‘ ayaṃ kho samaṇo gotamo cātuvaṇṇiṃ suddhiṃ paññapeti. 
866549,165,1324,51,64,1,71,11,Ko nu kho pahoti samaṇena gotamena saddhiṃ asmiṃ vacane paṭimantetun’’ ti? 
866550,165,1324,65,94,1,248,23,"Tena kho pana samayena assalāyano nāma māṇavo sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati daharo, vuttasiro, soḷasavassuddesiko jātiyā, tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ, padako, veyyākaraṇo, lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo. "
866551,165,1324,95,100,1,36,5,Atha kho tesaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ etadahosi–
866552,165,1324,101,123,1,125,15,"‘‘ ayaṃ kho assalāyano māṇavo sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati daharo, vuttasiro, soḷasavassuddesiko jātiyā, tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū… pe… anavayo. "
866553,165,1324,124,136,1,68,10,So kho pahoti samaṇena gotamena saddhiṃ asmiṃ vacane paṭimantetun’’ ti. 
866554,165,1325,2,10,1,58,8,Atha kho te brāhmaṇā yena assalāyano māṇavo tenupaṅkamiṃsu; 
