866556,165,1325,16,29,1,62,8,"‘‘ ayaṃ, bho assalāyana , samaṇo gotamo cātuvaṇṇiṃ suddhiṃ paññapeti. "
866557,165,1325,30,51,1,75,10,Etu bhavaṃ assalāyano samaṇena gotamena saddhiṃ asmiṃ vacane paṭimantetū’’ ti[ paṭimantetunti( pī. ka.)]. 
