866560,165,1326,22,27,1,44,5,dhammavādino ca pana duppaṭimantiyā bhavanti. 
866561,165,1326,28,39,1,68,9,Nāhaṃ sakkomi samaṇena gotamena saddhiṃ asmiṃ vacane paṭimantetun’’ ti. 
