866739,165,1352,2,4,1,16,2,4 . Ghoṭamukhasuttaṃ 
866740,165,1353,2,19,1,75,10,412. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā udeno bārāṇasiyaṃ viharati khemiyambavane. 
866741,165,1353,20,31,1,89,11,Tena kho pana samayena ghoṭamukho brāhmaṇo bārāṇasiṃ anuppatto hoti kenacideva karaṇīyena. 
866742,165,1353,32,43,1,106,10,Atha kho ghoṭamukho brāhmaṇo jaṅghāvihāraṃ anucaṅkamamāno anuvicaramāno yena khemiyambavanaṃ tenupasaṅkami. 
