866910,165,1380,22,55,1,184,22,"So‘ idaṃ dukkhan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti;"
