866931,165,1384,36,59,1,115,17,"Atthi ca me, bho udena, aṅgarājā devasikaṃ niccabhikkhaṃ dadāti , tato ahaṃ bhoto udenassa ekaṃ niccabhikkhaṃ dadāmī’’ ti."
866932,165,1384,60,75,1,63,9,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana te, brāhmaṇa, aṅgarājā devasikaṃ niccabhikkhaṃ dadātī’’ ti?"
