866934,165,1384,88,102,1,58,8,"‘‘ Na kho no, brāhmaṇa, kappati jātarūparajataṃ paṭiggahetun’’ ti."
866935,165,1384,103,118,1,72,11,‘‘ Sace taṃ bhoto udenassa na kappati vihāraṃ bhoto udenassa kārāpessāmī’’ ti.
866936,165,1384,119,139,1,95,12,"‘‘ Sace kho me tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, vihāraṃ, kārāpetukāmo, pāṭaliputte saṅghassa upaṭṭhānasālaṃ kārāpehī’’ ti."
866937,165,1384,140,155,1,105,13,‘‘ Imināpāhaṃ bhoto udenassa bhiyyosomattāya attamano abhiraddho yaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ udeno saṅghe dāne samādapeti. 
866938,165,1384,156,174,1,119,14,"Esāhaṃ, bho udena, etissā ca niccabhikkhāya aparāya ca niccabhikkhāya pāṭaliputte saṅghassa upaṭṭhānasālaṃ kārāpessāmī’’ ti. "
866939,165,1384,175,190,1,125,14,Atha kho ghoṭamukho brāhmaṇo etissā ca niccabhikkhāya aparāya ca niccabhikkhāya pāṭaliputte saṅghassa upaṭṭhānasālaṃ kārāpesi. 
