866941,165,1385,2,5,1,36,3,Ghoṭamukhasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ catutthaṃ.
866942,165,1386,2,4,1,11,2,5 . Caṅkīsuttaṃ 
866943,165,1387,2,29,1,144,18,422. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ yena opāsādaṃ nāma kosalānaṃ brāhmaṇagāmo tadavasari. 
866944,165,1387,30,39,1,72,9,Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā opāsāde viharati uttarena opāsādaṃ devavane sālavane. 
866945,165,1387,40,58,1,166,18,Tena kho pana samayena caṅkī brāhmaṇo opāsādaṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ raññā pasenadinā kosalena dinnaṃ rājadāyaṃ brahmadeyyaṃ. 
866946,165,1387,59,63,1,40,4,Assosuṃ kho opāsādakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā–
866947,165,1387,64,90,1,183,21,"‘‘ samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ opāsādaṃ anuppatto, opāsāde viharati uttarena opāsādaṃ devavane sālavane. "
866948,165,1387,91,100,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
866949,165,1387,101,118,1,142,15,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti. 
866950,165,1387,119,132,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
866951,165,1387,133,147,1,135,12,"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ, kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. "
866952,165,1387,148,158,1,53,8,Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’ ti. 
866953,165,1388,2,19,1,129,13,423. Atha kho opāsādakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā opāsādā nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī gaṇībhūtā uttarenamukhā gacchanti yena devavanaṃ sālavanaṃ. 
866954,165,1388,20,29,1,68,9,Tena kho pana samayena caṅkī brāhmaṇo uparipāsāde divāseyyaṃ upagato. 
866955,165,1388,30,46,1,155,16,Addasā kho caṅkī brāhmaṇo opāsādake brāhmaṇagahapatike opāsādā nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī gaṇībhūte uttarena mukhaṃ yena devavanaṃ sālavanaṃ tenupasaṅkamante. 
866956,165,1388,47,50,1,22,3,Disvā khattaṃ āmantesi–
866957,165,1388,51,74,1,145,17,"‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, bho khatte, opāsādakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā opāsādā nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī gaṇībhūtā uttarenamukhā gacchanti yena devavanaṃ sālavanan’’ ti?"
866958,165,1388,75,103,1,189,22,"‘‘ Atthi, bho caṅkī, samaṇo gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ opāsādaṃ anuppatto, opāsāde viharati uttarena opāsādaṃ devavane sālavane. "
866959,165,1388,104,113,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
866960,165,1388,114,131,1,142,15,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti. 
866961,165,1388,132,141,1,47,6,Tamete bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya gacchantī’’ ti.
866962,165,1388,142,154,1,66,8,"‘‘ Tena hi, bho khatte, yena opāsādakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tenupasaṅkama; "
866963,165,1388,155,161,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā opāsādake brāhmaṇagahapatike evaṃ vadehi–
866964,165,1388,162,184,1,109,14,"‘ caṅkī, bho, brāhmaṇo evamāha– āgamentu kira bhonto, caṅkīpi brāhmaṇo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī’’’ ti."
866965,165,1388,185,204,1,105,13,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti kho so khatto caṅkissa brāhmaṇassa paṭissutvā yena opāsādakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tenupasaṅkami; "
866966,165,1388,205,209,1,52,4,upasaṅkamitvā opāsādake brāhmaṇagahapatike etadavoca–
866967,165,1388,210,218,1,26,4,"‘‘ caṅkī, bho, brāhmaṇo evamāha–"
866968,165,1388,219,234,1,82,10,"‘ āgamentu kira bhonto, caṅkīpi brāhmaṇo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī’’’ ti. "
866969,165,1389,2,18,1,121,12,424. Tena kho pana samayena nānāverajjakānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ pañcamattāni brāhmaṇasatāni opāsāde paṭivasanti kenacideva karaṇīyena. 
866970,165,1389,19,23,1,23,4,Assosuṃ kho te brāhmaṇā–
866971,165,1389,24,36,1,64,8,‘‘ caṅkī kira brāhmaṇo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī’’ ti. 
866972,165,1389,37,45,1,57,8,Atha kho te brāhmaṇā yena caṅkī brāhmaṇo tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
866973,165,1389,46,50,1,41,4,upasaṅkamitvā caṅkiṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavocuṃ–
866974,165,1389,51,64,1,69,9,‘‘ saccaṃ kira bhavaṃ caṅkī samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī’’ ti?
866975,165,1389,65,74,1,20,5,"‘‘ Evaṃ kho me, bho, hoti–"
866976,165,1389,75,85,1,49,6,‘ ahaṃ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissāmī’’’ ti.
866977,165,1389,86,95,1,52,7,‘‘ Mā bhavaṃ caṅkī samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkami. 
866978,165,1389,96,104,1,63,8,Na arahati bhavaṃ caṅkī samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ; 
866979,165,1389,105,112,1,67,7,samaṇotveva gotamo arahati bhavantaṃ caṅkiṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ. 
866980,165,1389,113,128,1,125,15,Bhavañhi caṅkī ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena. 
866981,165,1389,129,156,1,206,25,"Yampi bhavaṃ caṅkī ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena, imināpaṅgena na arahati bhavaṃ caṅkī samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ; "
866982,165,1389,157,164,1,67,7,samaṇotveva gotamo arahati bhavantaṃ caṅkiṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ. 
866983,165,1389,165,292,1,903,95,"Bhavañhi caṅkī aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo… pe… bhavañhi caṅkī tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ, padako, veyyākaraṇo, lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo… pe… bhavañhi caṅkī abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato brahmavaṇṇī brahmavacchasī[ brahmavaccasī( sī. pī.)] akhuddāvakāso dassanāya… pe… bhavañhi caṅkī sīlavā vuddhasīlī vuddhasīlena samannāgato… pe… bhavañhi caṅkī kalyāṇavāco kalyāṇavākkaraṇo poriyā vācāya samannāgato vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā… pe… bhavañhi caṅkī bahūnaṃ ācariyapācariyo, tīṇi māṇavakasatāni mante vāceti… pe… bhavañhi caṅkī rañño pasenadissa kosalassa sakkato garukato mānito pūjito apacito… pe… bhavañhi caṅkī brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa sakkato garukato mānito pūjito apacito… pe… bhavañhi caṅkī opāsādaṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ raññā pasenadinā kosalena dinnaṃ rājadāyaṃ brahmadeyyaṃ. "
866984,165,1389,293,319,1,224,24,"Yampi bhavaṃ caṅkī opāsādaṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ raññā pasenadinā kosalena dinnaṃ rājadāyaṃ brahmadeyyaṃ, imināpaṅgena na arahati bhavaṃ caṅkī samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ; "
866985,165,1389,320,330,1,70,8,samaṇotveva gotamo arahati bhavantaṃ caṅkiṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamitun’’ ti. 
866986,165,1390,2,14,1,47,7,"425. Evaṃ vutte, caṅkī brāhmaṇo te brāhmaṇe etadavoca–"
866987,165,1390,15,33,1,93,13,"‘‘ tena hi, bho, mamapi suṇātha, yathā mayameva arahāma taṃ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ; "
866988,165,1390,34,42,1,64,8,natveva arahati so bhavaṃ gotamo amhākaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ. 
866989,165,1390,43,62,1,134,17,"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena. "
866990,165,1390,63,92,1,207,26,"Yampi, bho, samaṇo gotamo ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena, imināpaṅgena na arahati so bhavaṃ gotamo amhākaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ; "
866991,165,1390,93,115,1,71,9,atha kho mayameva arahāma taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ[ ettha dī. ni.1.304 aññampi guṇapadaṃ dissati]. 
866992,165,1390,116,330,1,1282,156,"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo pahūtaṃ hiraññasuvaṇṇaṃ ohāya pabbajito bhūmigatañca vehāsaṭṭhañca… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo daharova samāno yuvā susukāḷakeso bhadrena yobbanena samannāgato paṭhamena vayasā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo akāmakānaṃ mātāpitūnaṃ assumukhānaṃ rudantānaṃ kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato brahmavaṇṇī brahmavacchasī akhuddāvakāso dassanāya… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sīlavā ariyasīlī kusalasīlī kusalena sīlena samannāgato… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo kalyāṇavāco kalyāṇavākkaraṇo poriyā vācāya samannāgato vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo bahūnaṃ ācariyapācariyo… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo khīṇakāmarāgo vigatacāpallo… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo kammavādī kiriyavādī apāpapurekkhāro brahmaññāya pajāya… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo uccā kulā pabbajito asambhinnā khattiyakulā… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo aḍḍhā kulā pabbajito mahaddhanā mahābhogā… pe… samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ tiroraṭṭhā tirojanapadā saṃpucchituṃ āgacchanti… pe… samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ anekāni devatāsahassāni pāṇehi saraṇaṃ gatāni… pe… samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–"
866993,165,1390,331,438,1,566,71,"‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇehi samannāgato… pe…[ etthāpi dī. ni.1.304 aññānipi guṇapadānaṃ dissanti] samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ rājā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro saputtadāro pāṇehi saraṇaṃ gato… pe… samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ rājā pasenadi kosalo saputtadāro pāṇehi saraṇaṃ gato… pe… samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti saputtadāro pāṇehi saraṇaṃ gato… pe… samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo opāsādaṃ anuppatto opāsāde viharati uttarena opāsādaṃ devavane sālavane. "
866994,165,1390,439,454,1,82,14,"Ye kho te samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā amhākaṃ gāmakkhettaṃ āgacchanti, atithī no te honti. "
866995,165,1390,455,462,1,63,7,Atithī kho panamhehi sakkātabbā garukātabbā mānetabbā pūjetabbā. 
866996,165,1390,463,479,1,118,14,"Yampi samaṇo gotamo opāsādaṃ anuppatto opāsāde viharati uttarena opāsādaṃ devavane sālavane, atithimhākaṃ samaṇo gotamo. "
866997,165,1390,480,487,1,63,7,Atithi kho panamhehi sakkātabbo garukātabbo mānetabbo pūjetabbo. 
866998,165,1390,488,498,1,72,9,Imināpaṅgena na arahati so bhavaṃ gotamo amhākaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ; 
866999,165,1390,499,508,1,71,9,atha kho mayameva arahāma taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ. 
867000,165,1390,509,528,1,99,16,"Ettake kho ahaṃ, bho, tassa bhoto gotamassa vaṇṇe pariyāpuṇāmi, no ca kho so bhavaṃ gotamo ettakavaṇṇo; "
867001,165,1390,529,534,1,34,5,aparimāṇavaṇṇo hi so bhavaṃ gotamo. 
867002,165,1390,535,563,1,95,12,"Ekamekenapi tena[ ekamekenapi bho( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] aṅgena samannāgato na arahati, so, bhavaṃ gotamo amhākaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ; "
867003,165,1390,564,573,1,73,9,atha kho mayameva arahāma taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamitunti. 
867004,165,1390,574,588,1,70,10,"Tena hi, bho, sabbeva mayaṃ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissāmā’’ ti. "
867005,165,1391,2,17,1,80,10,426. Atha kho caṅkī brāhmaṇo mahatā brāhmaṇagaṇena saddhiṃ yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
867006,165,1391,18,22,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
867007,165,1391,23,29,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
867008,165,1391,30,47,1,121,16,Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā vuddhehi vuddhehi brāhmaṇehi saddhiṃ kiñci kiñci kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā nisinno hoti. 
867009,165,1391,48,94,1,253,25,"Tena kho pana samayena kāpaṭiko[ kāpaṭhiko( sī. pī.), kāpadiko( syā. kaṃ.)] nāma māṇavo daharo vuttasiro soḷasavassuddesiko jātiyā, tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ, padako, veyyākaraṇo, lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo tassaṃ parisāyaṃ nisinno hoti. "
867010,165,1391,95,105,1,94,10,So vuddhānaṃ vuddhānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ bhagavatā saddhiṃ mantayamānānaṃ antarantarā kathaṃ opāteti. 
867011,165,1391,106,112,1,44,6,Atha kho bhagavā kāpaṭikaṃ māṇavaṃ apasādeti–
867012,165,1391,113,124,1,92,9,‘‘ māyasmā bhāradvājo vuddhānaṃ vuddhānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ mantayamānānaṃ antarantarā kathaṃ opātetu. 
867013,165,1391,125,132,1,45,5,Kathāpariyosānaṃ āyasmā bhāradvājo āgametū’’ ti. 
867014,165,1391,133,140,1,47,6,"Evaṃ vutte, caṅkī brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–"
867015,165,1391,141,149,1,44,6,‘‘ mā bhavaṃ gotamo kāpaṭikaṃ māṇavaṃ apasādesi. 
867016,165,1391,150,183,1,198,27,"Kulaputto ca kāpaṭiko māṇavo, bahussuto ca kāpaṭiko māṇavo, paṇḍito ca kāpaṭiko māṇavo, kalyāṇavākkaraṇo ca kāpaṭiko māṇavo, pahoti ca kāpaṭiko māṇavo bhotā gotamena saddhiṃ asmiṃ vacane paṭimantetun’’ ti. "
867017,165,1391,184,189,1,28,4,Atha kho bhagavato etadahosi–
867018,165,1391,190,230,1,67,8,"‘‘ addhā kho kāpaṭikassa[ etadahosi‘‘ kāpaṭikassa( ka.)] māṇavassa tevijjake pāvacane kathā[ kathaṃ( sī. ka.), kathaṃ( syā. kaṃ. pī.)] bhavissati. "
867019,165,1391,231,239,1,41,6,Tathā hi naṃ brāhmaṇā saṃpurekkharontī’’ ti. 
867020,165,1391,240,246,1,40,5,Atha kho kāpaṭikassa māṇavassa etadahosi –
867021,165,1391,247,264,1,91,12,"‘‘ yadā me samaṇo gotamo cakkhuṃ upasaṃharissati, athāhaṃ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ pañhaṃ pucchissāmī’’ ti. "
867022,165,1391,265,278,1,114,13,Atha kho bhagavā kāpaṭikassa māṇavassa cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya yena kāpaṭiko māṇavo tena cakkhūni upasaṃhāsi. 
867023,165,1392,2,11,1,40,5,427. Atha kho kāpaṭikassa māṇavassa etadahosi–
867024,165,1392,12,19,1,35,5,‘‘ samannāharati kho maṃ samaṇo gotamo. 
867025,165,1392,20,28,1,47,6,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ pañhaṃ puccheyyan’’ ti. 
867026,165,1392,29,35,1,46,6,Atha kho kāpaṭiko māṇavo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
867027,165,1392,36,55,1,132,14,"‘‘ yadidaṃ, bho gotama, brāhmaṇānaṃ porāṇaṃ mantapadaṃ itihitihaparamparāya piṭakasampadāya, tattha ca brāhmaṇā ekaṃsena niṭṭhaṃ gacchanti–"
867028,165,1392,56,63,1,29,4,"‘ idameva saccaṃ, moghamaññan’ ti. "
867029,165,1392,64,71,1,28,5,Idha bhavaṃ gotamo kimāhā’’ ti?
867030,165,1392,72,85,1,67,9,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana, bhāradvāja, atthi koci brāhmaṇānaṃ ekabrāhmaṇopi yo evamāha–"
867031,165,1392,86,92,1,32,4,"‘ ahametaṃ jānāmi, ahametaṃ passāmi. "
867032,165,1392,93,101,1,29,4,"Idameva saccaṃ, moghamaññan’’’ ti?"
