867198,165,1416,2,20,1,87,11,436. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
867199,165,1416,21,28,1,52,7,Atha kho esukārī brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
867200,165,1416,29,33,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
867201,165,1416,34,40,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
867202,165,1416,41,48,1,60,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho esukārī brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
867203,165,1416,49,75,1,183,18,"‘‘ brāhmaṇā, bho gotama, catasso pāricariyā paññapenti– brāhmaṇassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti, khattiyassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti, vessassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti, suddassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti. "
867204,165,1416,76,85,1,63,7,"Tatridaṃ, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā brāhmaṇassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti–"
867205,165,1416,86,108,1,132,17,"‘ brāhmaṇo vā brāhmaṇaṃ paricareyya, khattiyo vā brāhmaṇaṃ paricareyya, vesso vā brāhmaṇaṃ paricareyya, suddo vā brāhmaṇaṃ paricareyyā’ ti. "
867206,165,1416,109,120,1,63,8,"Idaṃ kho, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā brāhmaṇassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti. "
867207,165,1416,121,130,1,63,7,"Tatridaṃ, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā khattiyassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti–"
867208,165,1416,131,148,1,98,13,"‘ khattiyo vā khattiyaṃ paricareyya, vesso vā khattiyaṃ paricareyya, suddo vā khattiyaṃ paricareyyā’ ti. "
867209,165,1416,149,159,1,63,8,"Idaṃ kho, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā khattiyassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti. "
