867211,165,1416,170,183,1,58,9,"‘ vesso vā vessaṃ paricareyya, suddo vā vessaṃ paricareyyā’ ti. "
867212,165,1416,184,195,1,60,8,"Idaṃ kho, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā vessassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti . "
867213,165,1416,196,205,1,60,7,"Tatridaṃ, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā suddassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti–"
867214,165,1416,206,210,1,26,3,‘ suddova suddaṃ paricareyya. 
867215,165,1416,211,217,1,34,5,Ko panañño suddaṃ paricarissatī’ ti? 
867216,165,1416,218,228,1,60,8,"Idaṃ kho, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā suddassa pāricariyaṃ paññapenti. "
867217,165,1416,229,238,1,53,7,"Brāhmaṇā, bho gotama, imā catasso pāricariyā paññapenti. "
867218,165,1416,239,246,1,28,5,Idha bhavaṃ gotamo kimāhā’’ ti? 
867219,165,1417,2,17,1,58,7,"437.‘‘ Kiṃ pana, brāhmaṇa, sabbo loko brāhmaṇānaṃ etadabbhanujānāti–"
867220,165,1417,18,36,1,36,5,‘ imā catasso pāricariyā paññapentū’’’ ti[ paññapentīti( sī. ka.)]?
867221,165,1417,37,46,1,19,4,"‘‘ No hidaṃ, bho gotama’’."
867222,165,1417,47,70,1,50,6,"‘‘ Seyyathāpi, brāhmaṇa, puriso daliddo[ daḷiddo( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] assako anāḷhiyo. "
867223,165,1417,71,75,1,31,4,Tassa akāmassa bilaṃ olaggeyyuṃ–
867224,165,1417,76,90,1,65,9,"‘ idaṃ te, ambho purisa, maṃsaṃ khāditabbaṃ, mūlañca anuppadātabban’ ti. "
867225,165,1417,91,107,1,110,13,"Evameva kho, brāhmaṇa, brāhmaṇā appaṭiññāya tesaṃ samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ, atha ca panimā catasso pāricariyā paññapenti. "
867226,165,1417,108,119,1,46,6,"Nāhaṃ, brāhmaṇa,‘ sabbaṃ paricaritabban’ ti vadāmi; "
867227,165,1417,120,131,1,49,7,"nāhaṃ, brāhmaṇa,‘ sabbaṃ na paricaritabban’ ti vadāmi. "
867228,165,1417,132,151,1,100,14,"Yaṃ hissa, brāhmaṇa, paricarato pāricariyāhetu pāpiyo assa na seyyo, nāhaṃ taṃ‘ paricaritabban’ ti vadāmi; "
867229,165,1417,152,169,1,102,13,"yañca khvāssa, brāhmaṇa, paricarato pāricariyāhetu seyyo assa na pāpiyo tamahaṃ‘ paricaritabban’ ti vadāmi. "
867230,165,1417,170,177,1,39,5,"Khattiyaṃ cepi, brāhmaṇa, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ–"
867231,165,1417,178,199,1,113,18,"‘ yaṃ vā te paricarato pāricariyāhetu pāpiyo assa na seyyo, yaṃ vā te paricarato pāricariyāhetu seyyo assa na pāpiyo; "
