867466,165,1459,2,17,1,103,11,449. Atha kho dhanañjāni brāhmaṇo āyasmato sāriputtassa bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi. 
867467,165,1459,18,28,1,81,10,Atha kho dhanañjāni brāhmaṇo aparena samayena ābādhiko ahosi dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. 
867468,165,1459,29,37,1,55,7,Atha kho dhanañjāni brāhmaṇo aññataraṃ purisaṃ āmantesi –
867469,165,1459,38,50,1,48,7,"‘‘ ehi tvaṃ, ambho purisa , yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkama; "
867470,165,1459,51,58,1,57,7,upasaṅkamitvā mama vacanena bhagavato pāde sirasā vandāhi–
867471,165,1459,59,68,1,56,6,"‘ dhanañjāni, bhante, brāhmaṇo ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. "
867472,165,1459,69,76,1,35,6,So bhagavato pāde sirasā vandatī’ ti. 
