867735,165,1609,2,19,1,87,11,462. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
867736,165,1609,20,34,1,126,14,Tena kho pana samayena subho māṇavo todeyyaputto sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati aññatarassa gahapatissa nivesane kenacideva karaṇīyena. 
867737,165,1609,35,47,1,96,12,Atha kho subho māṇavo todeyyaputto yassa gahapatissa nivesane paṭivasati taṃ gahapatiṃ etadavoca–
867738,165,1609,48,54,1,20,3,"‘‘ sutaṃ metaṃ, gahapati–"
867739,165,1609,55,61,1,31,4,‘ avivittā sāvatthī arahantehī’ ti. 
