867741,165,1609,74,86,1,72,8,"‘‘ Ayaṃ, bhante, bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
867742,165,1609,87,96,1,39,5,"Taṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ payirupāsassū’’ ti. "
867743,165,1609,97,109,1,90,11,Atha kho subho māṇavo todeyyaputto tassa gahapatissa paṭissutvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
867744,165,1609,110,114,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
867745,165,1609,115,121,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
867746,165,1609,122,130,1,69,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho subho māṇavo todeyyaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
867747,165,1609,131,139,1,30,4,"‘‘ brāhmaṇā, bho gotama, evamāhaṃsu–"
867748,165,1609,140,157,1,96,14,"‘ gahaṭṭho ārādhako hoti ñāyaṃ dhammaṃ kusalaṃ, na pabbajito ārādhako hoti ñāyaṃ dhammaṃ kusalan’ ti. "
867749,165,1609,158,165,1,28,5,Idha bhavaṃ gotamo kimāhā’’ ti? 
