867972,165,1653,2,4,1,15,2,10 . Saṅgāravasuttaṃ 
867973,165,1654,2,21,1,89,12,473. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ carati mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ. 
867974,165,1654,22,68,1,114,16,"Tena kho pana samayena dhanañjānī[ dhānañjānī( sī. pī.)] nāma brāhmaṇī cañcalikappe[ maṇḍalakappe( sī.), paccalakappe( syā. kaṃ.), caṇḍalakappe( pī.)] paṭivasati abhippasannā buddhe ca dhamme ca saṅghe ca. "
867975,165,1654,69,77,1,67,8,Atha kho dhanañjānī brāhmaṇī upakkhalitvā tikkhattuṃ udānaṃ udānesi–
867976,165,1654,78,85,1,46,5,‘‘ namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa. 
867977,165,1654,86,91,1,46,5,Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa. 
867978,165,1654,92,101,1,49,6,Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassā’’ ti . 
867979,165,1655,2,25,1,205,19,"Tena kho pana samayena saṅgāravo nāma māṇavo cañcalikappe paṭivasati tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ , padako, veyyākaraṇo, lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo. "
867980,165,1655,26,35,1,74,9,Assosi kho saṅgāravo māṇavo dhanañjāniyā brāhmaṇiyā evaṃ vācaṃ bhāsamānāya. 
867981,165,1655,36,40,1,37,4,Sutvā dhanañjāniṃ brāhmaṇiṃ etadavoca–
867982,165,1655,41,124,1,160,19,"‘‘ avabhūtāva ayaṃ[ avabhūtā cayaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] dhanañjānī brāhmaṇī, parabhūtāva ayaṃ[ parābhūtā cayaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] dhanañjānī brāhmaṇī, vijjamānānaṃ( tevijjānaṃ)[() sī. syā. kaṃ. pī. potthakesu natthi] brāhmaṇānaṃ, atha ca pana tassa muṇḍakassa samaṇakassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsissatī’’ ti[ bhāsatīti( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī)]."
867983,165,1655,125,139,1,68,10,"‘‘ Na hi pana tvaṃ, tāta bhadramukha, tassa bhagavato sīlapaññāṇaṃ jānāsi. "
867984,165,1655,140,165,1,149,18,"Sace tvaṃ, tāta bhadramukha, tassa bhagavato sīlapaññāṇaṃ jāneyyāsi, na tvaṃ, tāta bhadramukha, taṃ bhagavantaṃ akkositabbaṃ paribhāsitabbaṃ maññeyyāsī’’ ti."
867985,165,1655,166,186,1,83,13,"‘‘ Tena hi, bhoti, yadā samaṇo gotamo cañcalikappaṃ anuppatto hoti atha me āroceyyāsī’’ ti."
867986,165,1655,187,201,1,77,9,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhadramukhā’’ ti kho dhanañjānī brāhmaṇī saṅgāravassa māṇavassa paccassosi. "
867987,165,1656,2,12,1,83,10,Atha kho bhagavā kosalesu anupubbena cārikaṃ caramāno yena cañcalikappaṃ tadavasari. 
867988,165,1656,13,21,1,73,8,Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā cañcalikappe viharati todeyyānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ ambavane. 
867989,165,1656,22,26,1,30,4,Assosi kho dhanañjānī brāhmaṇī–
867990,165,1656,27,42,1,93,10,"‘‘ bhagavā kira cañcalikappaṃ anuppatto, cañcalikappe viharati todeyyānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ ambavane’’ ti. "
867991,165,1656,43,52,1,64,8,Atha kho dhanañjānī brāhmaṇī yena saṅgāravo māṇavo tenupasaṅkami ; 
867992,165,1656,53,57,1,42,4,upasaṅkamitvā saṅgāravaṃ māṇavaṃ etadavoca–
867993,165,1656,58,75,1,110,12,"‘‘ ayaṃ, tāta bhadramukha, so bhagavā cañcalikappaṃ anuppatto, cañcalikappe viharati todeyyānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ ambavane. "
867994,165,1656,76,86,1,43,6,"Yassadāni, tāta bhadramukha, kālaṃ maññasī’’ ti. "
867995,165,1657,2,23,1,94,12,"474.‘‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti kho saṅgāravo māṇavo dhanañjāniyā brāhmaṇiyā paṭissutvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
867996,165,1657,24,28,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
867997,165,1657,29,36,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
867998,165,1657,37,44,1,60,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho saṅgāravo māṇavo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
867999,165,1657,45,59,1,105,9,"‘‘ santi kho, bho gotama, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā diṭṭhadhammābhiññāvosānapāramippattā, ādibrahmacariyaṃ paṭijānanti. "
868000,165,1657,60,81,1,133,14,"Tatra, bho gotama, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā diṭṭhadhammābhiññāvosānapāramippattā, ādibrahmacariyaṃ paṭijānanti, tesaṃ bhavaṃ gotamo katamo’’ ti?"
868001,165,1657,82,96,1,109,8,"‘‘ Diṭṭhadhammābhiññāvosānapāramippattānaṃ, ādibrahmacariyaṃ paṭijānantānampi kho ahaṃ, bhāradvāja, vemattaṃ vadāmi. "
868002,165,1657,97,104,1,46,5,"Santi, bhāradvāja, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā anussavikā. "
868003,165,1657,105,111,1,79,5,"Te anussavena diṭṭhadhammābhiññāvosānapāramippattā, ādibrahmacariyaṃ paṭijānanti; "
868004,165,1657,112,115,1,27,3,seyyathāpi brāhmaṇā tevijjā. 
868005,165,1657,116,129,1,130,10,"Santi pana, bhāradvāja, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā kevalaṃ saddhāmattakena diṭṭhadhammābhiññāvosānapāramippattā, ādibrahmacariyaṃ paṭijānanti; "
868006,165,1657,130,133,1,24,3,seyyathāpi takkī vīmaṃsī. 
868007,165,1657,134,150,1,157,13,"Santi, bhāradvāja, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu sāmaṃyeva dhammaṃ abhiññāya diṭṭhadhammābhiññāvosānapāramippattā, ādibrahmacariyaṃ paṭijānanti. "
868008,165,1657,151,170,1,171,15,"Tatra, bhāradvāja, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu sāmaṃyeva dhammaṃ abhiññāya diṭṭhadhammābhiññāvosānapāramippattā, ādibrahmacariyaṃ paṭijānanti, tesāhamasmi. "
868009,165,1657,171,194,1,207,18,"Tadamināpetaṃ, bhāradvāja, pariyāyena veditabbaṃ, yathā ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu sāmaṃyeva dhammaṃ abhiññāya diṭṭhadhammābhiññāvosānapāramippattā, ādibrahmacariyaṃ paṭijānanti, tesāhamasmi. "
868010,165,1658,2,19,1,85,9,"475.‘‘ Idha me, bhāradvāja, pubbeva sambodhā anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva sato etadahosi–"
868011,165,1658,20,27,1,47,5,"‘ sambādho gharāvāso rajāpatho, abbhokāso pabbajjā. "
868012,165,1658,28,37,1,106,9,Nayidaṃ sukaraṃ agāraṃ ajjhāvasatā ekantaparipuṇṇaṃ ekantaparisuddhaṃ saṅkhalikhitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carituṃ. 
868013,165,1658,38,50,1,94,10,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajeyyan’ ti. 
868014,165,1658,51,81,1,241,26,"So kho ahaṃ, bhāradvāja, aparena samayena daharova samāno susukāḷakeso bhadrena yobbanena samannāgato paṭhamena vayasā akāmakānaṃ mātāpitūnaṃ assumukhānaṃ rudantānaṃ kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajiṃ. "
868015,165,1658,82,94,1,111,12,So evaṃ pabbajito samāno kiṃkusalagavesī anuttaraṃ santivarapadaṃ pariyesamāno yena āḷāro kālāmo tenupasaṅkamiṃ; 
868016,165,1658,95,99,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā āḷāraṃ kālāmaṃ etadavocaṃ–
