868459,166,27,108,117,1,80,8,"no ce sattā diṭṭhadhammūpakkamahetu sukhadukkhaṃ paṭisaṃvedenti, gārayhā nigaṇṭhā. "
868460,166,27,118,123,1,27,3,"Evaṃvādī, bhikkhave, nigaṇṭhā. "
868461,166,27,124,136,1,93,10,"Evaṃvādīnaṃ, bhikkhave, nigaṇṭhānaṃ ime dasa sahadhammikā vādānuvādā gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchanti. "
868462,166,27,137,148,1,56,8,"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, aphalo upakkamo hoti, aphalaṃ padhānaṃ. "
868463,166,28,2,18,1,58,7,"10.‘‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, saphalo upakkamo hoti, saphalaṃ padhānaṃ? "
868464,166,28,19,40,1,143,17,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na heva anaddhabhūtaṃ attānaṃ dukkhena addhabhāveti, dhammikañca sukhaṃ na pariccajati, tasmiñca sukhe anadhimucchito hoti. "
868465,166,28,41,44,1,16,3,So evaṃ pajānāti–
868466,166,28,45,67,1,156,19,"‘ imassa kho me dukkhanidānassa saṅkhāraṃ padahato saṅkhārappadhānā virāgo hoti, imassa pana me dukkhanidānassa ajjhupekkhato upekkhaṃ bhāvayato virāgo hotī’ ti. "
868467,166,28,68,99,1,109,13,"So yassa hi khvāssa[ yassa kho panassa( sī.), yassa khvāssa( pī.)] dukkhanidānassa saṅkhāraṃ padahato saṅkhārappadhānā virāgo hoti, saṅkhāraṃ tattha padahati. "
868468,166,28,100,112,1,98,11,"Yassa panassa dukkhanidānassa ajjhupekkhato upekkhaṃ bhāvayato virāgo hoti, upekkhaṃ tattha bhāveti. "
868469,166,28,113,127,1,112,13,Tassa tassa dukkhanidānassa saṅkhāraṃ padahato saṅkhārappadhānā virāgo hoti– evampissa taṃ dukkhaṃ nijjiṇṇaṃ hoti. 
868470,166,28,128,142,1,109,13,Tassa tassa dukkhanidānassa ajjhupekkhato upekkhaṃ bhāvayato virāgo hoti– evampissa taṃ dukkhaṃ nijjiṇṇaṃ hoti. 
868471,166,29,2,18,1,84,8,"11.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso itthiyā sāratto paṭibaddhacitto tibbacchando tibbāpekkho. "
868472,166,29,19,30,1,98,11,So taṃ itthiṃ passeyya aññena purisena saddhiṃ santiṭṭhantiṃ sallapantiṃ sañjagghantiṃ saṃhasantiṃ. 
868473,166,29,31,57,1,192,21,"Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, api nu tassa purisassa amuṃ itthiṃ disvā aññena purisena saddhiṃ santiṭṭhantiṃ sallapantiṃ sañjagghantiṃ saṃhasantiṃ uppajjeyyuṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassūpāyāsā’’ ti?"
868474,166,29,58,65,1,11,2,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’."
868475,166,29,66,73,1,14,3,‘‘ Taṃ kissa hetu’’?
868476,166,29,74,89,1,84,10,"‘‘ Amu hi, bhante, puriso amussā itthiyā sāratto paṭibaddhacitto tibbacchando tibbāpekkho . "
868477,166,29,90,107,1,147,14,Tasmā taṃ itthiṃ disvā aññena purisena saddhiṃ santiṭṭhantiṃ sallapantiṃ sañjagghantiṃ saṃhasantiṃ uppajjeyyuṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassūpāyāsā’’ ti.
868478,166,29,108,118,1,43,6,"‘‘ Atha kho, bhikkhave, tassa purisassa evamassa–"
868479,166,29,119,128,1,72,8,‘ ahaṃ kho amussā itthiyā sāratto paṭibaddhacitto tibbacchando tibbāpekkho. 
868480,166,29,129,144,1,147,14,Tassa me amuṃ itthiṃ disvā aññena purisena saddhiṃ santiṭṭhantiṃ sallapantiṃ sañjagghantiṃ saṃhasantiṃ uppajjanti sokaparidevadukkhadomanassūpāyāsā. 
868481,166,29,145,155,1,60,9,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ yo me amussā itthiyā chandarāgo taṃ pajaheyyan’ ti. 
868482,166,29,156,163,1,45,7,So yo amussā itthiyā chandarāgo taṃ pajaheyya. 
868483,166,29,164,177,1,115,13,So taṃ itthiṃ passeyya aparena samayena aññena purisena saddhiṃ santiṭṭhantiṃ sallapantiṃ sañjagghantiṃ saṃhasantiṃ. 
868484,166,29,178,203,1,192,21,"Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, api nu tassa purisassa amuṃ itthiṃ disvā aññena purisena saddhiṃ santiṭṭhantiṃ sallapantiṃ sañjagghantiṃ saṃhasantiṃ uppajjeyyuṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassūpāyāsā’’ ti?"
868485,166,29,204,212,1,15,3,"‘‘ No hetaṃ, bhante’’."
868486,166,29,213,220,1,14,3,‘‘ Taṃ kissa hetu’’?
868487,166,29,221,232,1,42,7,"‘‘ Amu hi, bhante, puriso amussā itthiyā virāgo. "
868488,166,29,233,250,1,150,15,Tasmā taṃ itthiṃ disvā aññena purisena saddhiṃ santiṭṭhantiṃ sallapantiṃ sañjagghantiṃ saṃhasantiṃ na uppajjeyyuṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassūpāyāsā’’ ti.
868489,166,30,2,26,1,150,19,"‘ ‘ Evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na heva anaddhabhūtaṃ attānaṃ dukkhena addhabhāveti, dhammikañca sukhaṃ na pariccajati, tasmiñca sukhe anadhimucchito hoti. "
868490,166,30,27,30,1,16,3,So evaṃ pajānāti–
868491,166,30,31,53,1,156,19,"‘ imassa kho me dukkhanidānassa saṅkhāraṃ padahato saṅkhārappadhānā virāgo hoti, imassa pana me dukkhanidānassa ajjhupekkhato upekkhaṃ bhāvayato virāgo hotī’ ti. "
868492,166,30,54,68,1,109,13,"So yassa hi khvāssa dukkhanidānassa saṅkhāraṃ padahato saṅkhārappadhānā virāgo hoti, saṅkhāraṃ tattha padahati; "
868493,166,30,69,81,1,98,11,"yassa panassa dukkhanidānassa ajjhupekkhato upekkhaṃ bhāvayato virāgo hoti, upekkhaṃ tattha bhāveti. "
868494,166,30,82,98,1,112,13,Tassa tassa dukkhanidānassa saṅkhāraṃ padahato saṅkhārappadhānā virāgo hoti– evampissa taṃ dukkhaṃ nijjiṇṇaṃ hoti . 
