868497,166,31,2,16,1,50,6,"12.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu iti paṭisañcikkhati–"
868498,166,31,17,29,1,82,10,"‘ yathāsukhaṃ kho me viharato akusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti, kusalā dhammā parihāyanti; "
868499,166,31,30,42,1,88,11,"dukkhāya pana me attānaṃ padahato akusalā dhammā parihāyanti, kusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti. "
868500,166,31,43,49,1,41,5,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ dukkhāya attānaṃ padaheyyan’ ti. 
868501,166,31,50,54,1,28,4,So dukkhāya attānaṃ padahati. 
868502,166,31,55,67,1,86,10,Tassa dukkhāya attānaṃ padahato akusalā dhammā parihāyanti kusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti. 
868503,166,31,68,75,1,48,7,So na aparena samayena dukkhāya attānaṃ padahati. 
868504,166,31,76,79,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
868505,166,31,80,95,1,96,13,"Yassa hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu atthāya dukkhāya attānaṃ padaheyya svāssa attho abhinipphanno hoti. "
868506,166,31,96,103,1,51,7,Tasmā na aparena samayena dukkhāya attānaṃ padahati. 
868507,166,31,104,117,1,92,11,"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, usukāro tejanaṃ dvīsu alātesu ātāpeti paritāpeti ujuṃ karoti kammaniyaṃ. "
868508,166,31,118,157,1,198,27,"Yato kho, bhikkhave, usukārassa tejanaṃ dvīsu alātesu ātāpitaṃ hoti paritāpitaṃ ujuṃ kataṃ[ ujuṃ kataṃ hoti( sī.)] kammaniyaṃ, na so taṃ aparena samayena usukāro tejanaṃ dvīsu alātesu ātāpeti paritāpeti ujuṃ karoti kammaniyaṃ. "
868509,166,31,158,161,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
868510,166,31,162,183,1,136,18,"Yassa hi so, bhikkhave, atthāya usukāro tejanaṃ dvīsu alātesu ātāpeyya paritāpeyya ujuṃ kareyya kammaniyaṃ svāssa attho abhinipphanno hoti. "
868511,166,31,184,197,1,97,13,Tasmā na aparena samayena usukāro tejanaṃ dvīsu alātesu ātāpeti paritāpeti ujuṃ karoti kammaniyaṃ. 
868512,166,31,198,206,1,49,6,"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu iti paṭisañcikkhati–"
868513,166,31,207,219,1,82,10,"‘ yathāsukhaṃ kho me viharato akusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti, kusalā dhammā parihāyanti; "
868514,166,31,220,232,1,88,11,"dukkhāya pana me attānaṃ padahato akusalā dhammā parihāyanti, kusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti. "
868515,166,31,233,239,1,41,5,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ dukkhāya attānaṃ padaheyyan’ ti. 
868516,166,31,240,244,1,28,4,So dukkhāya attānaṃ padahati. 
868517,166,31,245,256,1,86,10,"Tassa dukkhāya attānaṃ padahato akusalā dhammā parihāyanti, kusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti. "
868518,166,31,257,265,1,48,7,So na aparena samayena dukkhāya attānaṃ padahati. 
