868520,166,31,270,285,1,96,13,"Yassa hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu atthāya dukkhāya attānaṃ padaheyya svāssa attho abhinipphanno hoti. "
868521,166,31,286,293,1,51,7,Tasmā na aparena samayena dukkhāya attānaṃ padahati. 
868522,166,31,294,304,1,56,7,"Evampi, bhikkhave, saphalo upakkamo hoti, saphalaṃ padhānaṃ. "
868523,166,32,2,28,1,175,18,"13.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idha tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā. "
868524,166,32,29,42,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
868525,166,32,43,57,1,135,12,"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ, kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. "
868526,166,32,58,70,1,78,11,Taṃ dhammaṃ suṇāti gahapati vā gahapatiputto vā aññatarasmiṃ vā kule paccājāto. 
868527,166,32,71,78,1,50,7,So taṃ dhammaṃ sutvā tathāgate saddhaṃ paṭilabhati. 
868528,166,32,79,85,1,57,6,So tena saddhāpaṭilābhena samannāgato iti paṭisañcikkhati–
868529,166,32,86,93,1,47,5,"‘ sambādho gharāvāso rajāpatho, abbhokāso pabbajjā. "
868530,166,32,94,103,1,106,9,Nayidaṃ sukaraṃ agāraṃ ajjhāvasatā ekantaparipuṇṇaṃ ekantaparisuddhaṃ saṅkhalikhitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carituṃ. 
868531,166,32,104,116,1,94,10,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajeyyan’ ti. 
