869032,166,112,159,193,1,188,24,"‘ khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ ti pajānāmā’’ ti, kacci te, bhante, bhikkhū sammadeva aññaṃ byākaṃsu udāhu santetthekacce bhikkhū adhimānena aññaṃ byākaṃsūti? "
869033,166,113,2,18,1,53,8,"56.‘‘ Ye te, sunakkhatta, bhikkhū mama santike aññaṃ byākaṃsu–"
869034,166,113,19,38,1,82,11,"‘ khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ ti pajānāmā’’ ti ."
869035,166,113,39,59,1,102,11,"‘‘ Santetthekacce bhikkhū sammadeva aññaṃ byākaṃsu, santi panidhekacce bhikkhū adhimānenapi[ adhimānena(?)] aññaṃ byākaṃsu. "
869036,166,113,60,74,1,79,12,"Tatra, sunakkhatta, ye te bhikkhū sammadeva aññaṃ byākaṃsu tesaṃ taṃ tatheva hoti; "
869037,166,113,75,89,1,85,12,"ye pana te bhikkhū adhimānena aññaṃ byākaṃsu tatra, sunakkhatta, tathāgatassa evaṃ hoti–"
869038,166,113,90,105,1,25,4,‘ dhammaṃ nesaṃ desessan’ ti[ deseyyanti( pī. ka.)]. 
869039,166,113,106,112,1,40,4,"Evañcettha, sunakkhatta, tathāgatassa hoti–"
869040,166,113,113,119,1,25,4,‘ dhammaṃ nesaṃ desessan’ ti. 
869041,166,113,120,130,1,106,10,Atha ca panidhekacce moghapurisā pañhaṃ abhisaṅkharitvā abhisaṅkharitvā tathāgataṃ upasaṅkamitvā pucchanti. 
869042,166,113,131,140,1,46,6,"Tatra, sunakkhatta, yampi tathāgatassa evaṃ hoti–"
869043,166,113,141,153,1,53,8,‘ dhammaṃ nesaṃ desessan’ ti tassapi hoti aññathattan’’ ti.
869044,166,113,154,168,1,66,10,"‘‘ Etassa bhagavā kālo, etassa sugata kālo, yaṃ bhagavā dhammaṃ deseyya. "
869045,166,113,169,176,1,38,5,Bhagavato sutvā bhikkhū dhāressantī’’ ti.
869046,166,113,177,189,1,49,7,"‘‘ Tena hi, sunakkhatta suṇāhi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi ; "
869047,166,113,190,194,1,13,2,bhāsissāmī’’ ti.
869048,166,113,195,208,1,65,8,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti kho sunakkhatto licchaviputto bhagavato paccassosi. "
869049,166,113,209,211,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca– 
869050,166,114,2,16,1,34,5,"57.‘‘ Pañca kho ime, sunakkhatta, kāmaguṇā. "
869051,166,114,17,19,1,12,2,Katame pañca? 
869052,166,114,20,56,1,242,28,"Cakkhuviññeyyā rūpā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā, sotaviññeyyā saddā… pe… ghānaviññeyyā gandhā… jivhāviññeyyā rasā… kāyaviññeyyā phoṭṭhabbā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā– ime kho, sunakkhatta, pañca kāmaguṇā. "
869053,166,115,2,21,1,88,10,"58.‘‘ Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, sunakkhatta, vijjati yaṃ idhekacco purisapuggalo lokāmisādhimutto assa. "
869054,166,115,22,46,1,171,18,"Lokāmisādhimuttassa kho, sunakkhatta, purisapuggalassa tappatirūpī ceva kathā saṇṭhāti, tadanudhammañca anuvitakketi, anuvicāreti, tañca purisaṃ bhajati, tena ca vittiṃ āpajjati; "
869055,166,115,47,88,1,159,24,"āneñjapaṭisaṃyuttāya ca pana kathāya kacchamānāya na sussūsati, na sotaṃ odahati, na aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhāpeti[ upaṭṭhapeti( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)], na ca taṃ purisaṃ bhajati, na ca tena vittiṃ āpajjati. "
869056,166,115,89,101,1,76,10,"Seyyathāpi, sunakkhatta, puriso sakamhā gāmā vā nigamā vā ciravippavuttho assa. "
869057,166,115,102,112,1,68,10,So aññataraṃ purisaṃ passeyya tamhā gāmā vā nigamā vā acirapakkantaṃ. 
869058,166,115,113,125,1,95,12,So taṃ purisaṃ tassa gāmassa vā nigamassa vā khematañca subhikkhatañca appābādhatañca puccheyya; 
869059,166,115,126,139,1,95,12,tassa so puriso tassa gāmassa vā nigamassa vā khematañca subhikkhatañca appābādhatañca saṃseyya. 
869060,166,115,140,172,1,162,24,"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sunakkhatta, api nu so puriso tassa purisassa sussūseyya, sotaṃ odaheyya, aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhāpeyya, tañca purisaṃ bhajeyya, tena ca vittiṃ āpajjeyyā’’ ti?"
