869102,166,120,45,86,1,29,4,"Evaṃmāni[ evaṃmānī( sī. pī. ka.), evamādi( syā. kaṃ.)] assa atathaṃ samānaṃ[ atthaṃ samānaṃ( syā. kaṃ. pī.), atthasamānaṃ( sī.)]. "
