869113,166,121,65,86,1,64,9,"‘ ambho purisa, ubbhataṃ kho te sallaṃ, apanīto visadoso saupādiseso[ anupādiseso( sabbattha) ayampi tathāgatassa visayo]. "
869114,166,121,87,90,1,22,3,Analañca te antarāyāya. 
869115,166,121,91,104,1,89,12,"Sappāyāni ceva bhojanāni bhuñjeyyāsi, mā te asappāyāni bhojanāni bhuñjato vaṇo assāvī assa. "
869116,166,121,105,131,1,176,23,"Kālena kālañca vaṇaṃ dhoveyyāsi, kālena kālaṃ vaṇamukhaṃ ālimpeyyāsi, mā te na kālena kālaṃ vaṇaṃ dhovato na kālena kālaṃ vaṇamukhaṃ ālimpato pubbalohitaṃ vaṇamukhaṃ pariyonandhi. "
869117,166,121,132,146,1,102,13,"Mā ca vātātape cārittaṃ anuyuñji, mā te vātātape cārittaṃ anuyuttassa rajosūkaṃ vaṇamukhaṃ anuddhaṃsesi. "
869118,166,121,147,172,1,54,7,"Vaṇānurakkhī ca, ambho purisa, vihareyyāsi vaṇasāropī’ ti[ vaṇassāropīti( ka.) vaṇa+ saṃ+ ropī= vaṇasāropī-iti padavibhāgo]. "
869119,166,121,173,175,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
