869264,166,136,83,91,1,63,6,"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyā ākiñcaññāyatanasappāyā paṭipadā akkhāyati."
869265,166,137,2,12,1,54,7,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako iti paṭisañcikkhati–"
